name: Goroutine leak in websocket handler
description: WebSocket disconnect handler not cancelling context, leaving goroutines blocked on channel read. Goroutine count grows linearly with disconnects until OOM.
prompt:
Alert: websocket-gateway memory usage at 85% and climbing steadily.
Pod restarts happening every ~4 hours due to OOM.
No traffic increase. CPU normal. Connection count stable at ~5000.
Started 2 days ago after deploy v3.8.0.
Investigate and find the root cause.
